Project Description
Enferno.Public is a .NET library for infrastructural plumming, like logging, caching and inversion of control.
This is used when building applications that call

The project exposes three separate functional units, each accessible as its own NuGet-package.
  • Enferno.Public
Enferno.Public requires Enterprise library logging application block 5.x
This library is used by the following projects:
https://enfernostormapiclient.codeplex.com
Use Nuget - Enferno.Public is only available via NuGet. http://nuget.org/List/Packages/Enferno.Public.
PM> Install-Package Enferno.Public
  • Enferno.Public.Azure
Support functions for Azure specific considerations.
Use Nuget - Enferno.Public.Azure is only available via NuGet. http://www.nuget.org/packages/Enferno.Public.Azure
PM> Install-Package Enferno.Public.Azure
  • Enferno.Public.Logging
Logging specific support functions. As of now there are also logging specific functionality left in Enferno.Public that will be move into this project eventually.
Use Nuget - Enferno.Public.Logging is only available via NuGet. http://www.nuget.org/packages/Enferno.Public.Logging
PM> Install-Package Enferno.Public.Logging
  • Enferno.Public.Web
Contains models, mappers and repository, among others, for use in front-end applications,
Use Nuget - Enferno.Public.Web is only available via NuGet. http://www.nuget.org/packages/Enferno.Public.Web
PM> Install-Package Enferno.Public.Web
  • Enferno.Public.Web.ShoppingBasket
Contains viewmodels and typescript for use in front-end applications,
Use Nuget - Enferno.Public.Web.ShoppingBasket is only available via NuGet. http://www.nuget.org/packages/Enferno.Public.Web.ShoppingBasket
PM> Install-Package Enferno.Public.Web.ShoppingBasket
